        "$:/plugins/Cardo/help/ConversationHelp": {
            "text": "@@.help

!!!Conversations let you track your communications with other people. 

You can mark Conversations as being ''Phone'', ''Email'', ''Text'' (messaging), or ''Face-To-Face''.

{{$:/plugins/Cardo/images/calendar-x}}Log the date of the conversation by clicking on the calendar icon. When the date is set and shown, click on the ''[x]'' to clear it.

Use the ''Person:'' dropdown to indicate who the conversation was with.

@@
